rows.label: tlk001001_07_msg0001
rows.name:
I thank you not as an emperor,
but as an individual.

rows.label: tlk001001_07_msg0002
rows.name:
For continuing to travel with
Special Inquisitor Meleph and...

rows.label: tlk001001_07_msg0003
rows.name:
No... thank you for continuing
to travel with my sister.

rows.label: tlk001001_07_msg0004
rows.name:
The future depends on you.
Please continue to look after
my sister until the very end.

rows.label: tlk001001_07_msg0005
rows.name:
Sister... Please leave
Superbia's affairs to me.

rows.label: tlk001001_07_msg0006
rows.name:
Sister, please save Alst
together with the Heaven's
Holy Grail and Rex-san.

rows.label: tlk001001_07_msg0007
rows.name:
When everything has settled
down, I look forward to hearing
the stories of your journey.
